  DISPATCH --> DIFF
  DISPATCH --> DASH

  CONTRACTS -.type surface.-> DISPATCH
  CONTRACTS -.shared schemas.-> SNAP
  CONTRACTS -.adapter shapes.-> APPDOMAINS

  DOCTOR --> PROJECT
